Joint 1
.RS 4
shoulder
.RE
.PP
Joint 2
.RS 4
elbow
.RE
.PP
Joint 3
.RS 4
wrist (+ is wrist up & rotate hand)
.RE
.PP
Joint 4
.RS 4
wrist (+ is wrist down & rotate hand)
.RE
.PP
Joint 5
.RS 4
unused
.RE
.PP
Joint 6
.RS 4
unused
.RE
.PP
Joint 7
.RS 4
hand open/close (+ is close)
.RE
